            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>What's New in 0.1.3</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Control Center can now stay on top of other windows with the new Always on Top option.</li>
                        <li>Long-pressing dials and buttons in Control Center now triggers quick secondary actions.</li>
                        <li>AI mode indicators now use clean icons instead of text badges throughout the app.</li>
